{{Han etym}}

Found in various historical dictionaries such as {{w|Yupian}} 《{{w2|zh|玉篇}}》 and {{w|Guangyun}} 《{{w2|zh|廣韻}}》.

In the 1956 first round revision table of variant Chinese characters ({{w2|zh|第一批异体字整理表}}) by the People's Republic of China, {{l|zh|蒞}} and {{l|zh|涖}} were listed as {{w|Variant Chinese characters|variant forms}} that were replaced by <big>莅</big> as the orthodox form.  <!-- Refer https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/第一批异体字整理表/1955年 -->
